####################################################
#     xsmtp - A simple realization of smtp protocol
#
# Author: Bill Xia
# Blog: http://ibillxia.github.com
# Email: ibillxia@gmail.com
####################################################

This program is a simple mail dispatcher via smtp protocol. It runs only on Linux/Unix plantforms.
For more about pop3 and it's RFC documents, please refer to wiki: 
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Simple_Mail_Transfer_Protocol

